# evcxr-typst sidecar output (generated by the CLI)
.evcxr-typst-cache/

# Local source-mdBook checkout for the rust-by-example port (D-022).
# Tooling reads from this path; never vendored.
.rust-by-example/

# Local read-only checkout of upstream evcxr (the path-dep target during dev,
# per D-006 / D-025). Should not be committed into evcxr-typst.
.evcxr/

# Local read-only checkout of typst-community/prequery, kept as a reference
# for the prequery / metadata-emission pattern. Never vendored.
.prequery/

# Local read-only checkout of typst-community/wasm-minimal-protocol, kept
# as a reference for the Typst WASM plugin protocol (T-S04 / D-001). Never
# vendored.
.typst-wasm-minimal-protocol/
